Package mph.beans.dto

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    DataTransferObject
    This interface let an object to represent a Data Transfer Object.
    EntityDTO
    This interface is implemented by all the DTO classes.
    It extends DataTransferObject.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ArtifactDTO
    This class contains the information about an artifact.
    It implements the EntityDTO interface.
    CourseDTO
    This class contains the information about a course.
    It implements the EntityDTO interface.
    DeliverableDTO
    This class contains the information about a project deliverable.
    It implements the EntityDTO interface.
    IncomingFileDTO
    This class contains the information about an incoming file.
    It implements the DataTransferObject interface.
    OutcomingFileDTO
    This class contains the information about an outgoing file.
    It implements the DataTransferObject interface.
    PasswordHashDTO
    This class is used to store the MD5 hash of a password.
    It implements the DataTransferObject interface.
    ProfessorDTO
    This class contains the information about a professor.
    It extends UserDTO.
    ProjectDTO
    This class contains the information about a project.
    It implements the EntityDTO interface.
    StudentDTO
    This class contains the information about a student.
    It extends UserDTO.
    TeamDTO
    This class contains the information about a project team.
    It implements the EntityDTO interface.
    UserDTO
    This abstract class will be extended by the DTO's containing the information about a user.
    It implements the EntityDTO interface.
